\id INT I- NG Arop Translation 
\rem For a good example of INT book, see GNTD. 
\c 1 
\periph TransferPrimer|id="transferprimer" 
\mt1 Pasin bilong ritim tokples Arop 
\p Pasin bilong ritim tokples Arop i klostu wankain olsem pasin bilong ritim Tok Pisin. Tasol i gat wan wan samting i narakain liklik. 
\s1 Ol leta i narakain liklik long tok pisin 
\s2 P na B 
\p Yumi gat sampela tok i gat dispela leta \fq p\fq*, olsem \fq prum\fq*. Long tokples bilong yumi, \fq p\fq* na \fq b\fq* i wankain. Olsem na sampela taim yumi save raitim \fq prum\fq* na sampela taim yumi save raitim \fq brum\fq*. Mipela skelim olsem: yumi mas raitim wanpela na maski long narapela. Olsem na mipela save raitim \fq p\fq* tasol. 
\s2 yl na yn 
\p Sampela tok bilong yumi i no krai olsem tok pisin. Wanpela yumi gat long tok <<pis.>> Mipela save raitim \fq piyl\fq*. Dispela i no krai olsem \fqa pil\fqa*, nogat. Olsem na yumi mas painim rot bilong raitim. Lukim tupela leta \fq yl\fq*. Dispela tupela leta i krai olsem wanpela leta. 
\p Em wankain olsem long tok wara. Mipela save raitim \fq raiyn\fq*. Dispela \fq yn\fq* em i krai olsem wanpela leta. 
\s2 Glottal Stop 
\p Tokples bilong yumi i gat wanpela moa leta i no krai olsem Tok Pisin. Nem bilong dispela leta em i <<glottal stop.>> Dispela i stap namel long dispela tok bilong <<hevi>> (\fq perꞌian\fq*) na <<bilong em>> (\fq yiꞌe\fq*). Wok bilong dispela glottal stop em i olsem. Planti toktok long tokples i wankain. Taim dispela glottal stop i stap, em i save soim yumi dispela toktok i no wankain olsem narapela toktok. Wanpela em i olsem dispela tupela tok: \fq koron\fq* (<<ol i stap>>) na \fq korꞌon\fq* (<<ol i pasim>>). Sapos yumi raitim wankain tasol, bai yumi paol gen taim yumi ritim. Mipela save raitim dispela leta olgeta taim em i save kamap namel long wanpela tok. 
\p Tasol sapos em i kamap long stat bilong wanpela tok, mipela save lusim. Long wanem, mipela ting sapos dispela leta i stap long stat long wanpela tok, em bai paolim yumi. Olsem na mipela save raitim olsem: \fq Yi usia amana tektek\fq*. Dispela tok \fq usia\fq* i gat glottal stop long en, tasol mipela i lusim. Tasol sapos i stap namel long wanpela tok, em bai olsem: \fq Re korꞌusia amana tektek\fq*. \fq Korꞌusia\fq* i gat glottal stop. Nogut yu paol. Taim yu raitim, tingim gut pastaim. 
\p Mipela i no save putim glottal stop namel long taim tupela hap tok i save kam wantaim. Olsem \fq termen\fq*, i no gat glottal stop long en. No ken raitim olsem: \fqa terꞌmen\fqa*. 
\p I gat planti kain kain tok i gat glottal stop long ol. \fq Kraisꞌe\fq* (bilong Krais) \fq kaꞌar\fq* (em i bin raitim), \fq ya’e\fq* (bilong mi), \fq merꞌer\fq* (stret), \fq yi’e\fq* (bilong em), \fq ekꞌepesie\fq* (yu lusim), \fq takꞌakai\fq* (em i save opim), \fq waꞌiw\fq* (i go daun), \fq Godꞌe\fq* (bilong God), \fq terꞌestek \fq*(ol i beten), \fq keꞌep\fq* (em i gat), \fq arꞌaiyn\fq* (ol bai kaikai), na i gat planti moa. 
\s1 Tupela leta i wok bung wantaim 
\p Mipela i gat sampela tok i gat tupela leta i wok bung wantaim, olsem tupela ‘a’ i stap long \fq taako\fq*, \fq aan\fq*, na \fq aampia\fq*. Taim yumi gat tupela i wok bung wantaim olsem, mipela save raitim tupela. Sapos yu harim gut dispela ol tok, bai yu luksave olsem i gat tupela leta long en. 
\p Sampela taim tupela leta i bung wantaim tasol i no wankain. Olsem \fq joene\fq*, \fq soene\fq*, \fq kouw\fq* (karim samting). 
\s1 Brukim toktok 
\p Taim yumi toktok, yumi toktok tasol. Tasol taim yumi raitim tokples, yumi mas brukim ol toktok i go hap hap inap yumi ken ritim olsem ol i mekim long Tok Pisin na Inglis. Tasol i save hat liklik long luksave long wanem hap long brukim. 
\p Sapos yumi laik raitim <<ol i stap,>> yumi ken raitim olsem: \fqa rekermen\fqa*. Em i no hatwok long ritim. Tasol sapos yumi senisim i go long <<ol i no stap,>> em bai olsem: \fqa relinkermen\fqa*. Em longpela tumas. Olsem na mipela save brukim olsem: \fq re kermen\fq* na \fqa re lin kermen\fqa*. Mipela ting dispela em isi tru long ritim. 
\p Sampela tok i save bung wantaim narapela tok na senisim mining bilong en. Olsem na yu ken putim \fq mana\fq* i go wantaim \fq re kermen\fq* na i kamap olsem: \fq re kermenmana\fq*. Sapos yu harim gut, yu ken luksave olsem \fq kermenmana\fq* em wanpela tok tasol. Mipela save raitim olsem wanpela tok. 
\s1 Taim ol samting i lus 
\p Sampela taim, yumi toktok kwiktaim na yumi save lusim sampela liklik hap tok. Olsem yumi no save tok: \fq Et atwa Aitape\fq*. Mipela save tok olsem: \fq E atwa Aitape\fq*. Dispela <<\fq t\fq*>> bilong <<\fq et\fq*>> yumi save lusim. Tasol, taim yumi raitim dispela tok, yumi raitim dispela \fq t\fq* i go insait. Tasol taim yumi ritim, yumi ken abrusim. 
\p Narapela em i dispela tok <<\fq elin\fq*.>> Taim yumi tok <<ol i no kam,>> yumi save tok olsem: \fq re lin karama\fq*. Yumi save lusim e bilong elin. Taim yumi raitim, yumi lusim tu. 
\s1 Ol samting i krai klostu wankain 
\p Yumi gat tripela tok i krai klostu wankain. Em tok bilong sospen, yes, na maunten. Mipela save raitim olsem: 
\s1 Narapela nupela leta 
\p Yumi gat narapela leta i no gat long Tok Pisin. Em i no olsem \fq u\fq* na em i no olsem \fq o\fq*. Em i stap namel long tupela. Olsem na i hat liklik long raitim. Mipela save raitim olsem: \fq oo\fq*, olsem <<haus>> \fq onoo\fq*. No ken wari! Dispela leta i no save kamap planti taim. (Tasol i gat wanpela narapela tok \fq ono\fq* <<dispela,>> yu no ken paol long dispela tupela tok.) 
\periph Preface|id="preface" 
\mt1 Aij Kistekna 
\is1 Aij kistekna iyn o tartar koron buk soene olonma. 
\is2 Re aij welen welen tartar koron buk ene 
\ip 
\v 1 Pene e akniaw kamtaw re aij koron buk ene, e koluon akniawpaij pene buk soene, elin keꞌep re aij iyn buk Baibel peyian, elin. Yi keꞌep aij tartar ke re piksa koron iyn awro alpim e iyn akniawpaij re aij pene e na tekꞌies ene. Pene e koluon akꞌies re aij kistekna reꞌe o soenere. 
\is2 Aij takwa watan 
\ip 
\v 2 Baibel buk ponpontenen kermen olonma ene kerꞌep aij opeyian iyn akwa watan. Aij soene tekeswawna re o pene buk ono kes, ke re o elen omon et mas ato sawe na re tem iyn et tetpiyl atꞌes buk soono. 
\is2 Re aij noꞌuan 
\ip 
\v 3 Aij ononre tartar ene kerꞌep aij noꞌuan ke kerꞌep blakpla rait na koron re ono iyn artuiynjuiyna e nempeyian prum re o teweiyn aij soene na teresna ene. O taako iyn aij noꞌuare ene, iyn awo alpim e iyn aktirna re aij e tekpiyl akniaw ono prem ektek. 
\is2 Re Futnot — Aij kistekna iyn re o elin karama nempeyian 
\ip 
\v 4 Re taw elen iyn ves elen, e akniaw re leta welen awron.\f + \fr 1.0 \ft Aij ene futnot taako. O ene ekmen iyn awespaij aij remien reꞌe aij elen kermen ves taako. \f* Pene akniaw taon iyn pas ene, akniaw aij kistekna ekmen. Aij kistekna ene <<futnot>> taako. O soenere koron iyn artuiynjuiyna pene aij ononre elen koron pepa ene taon pet iyn akꞌies iyn awro alpim e iyn awkuo sawe kamtawna aij pene akon ves soene o awtuiynjuiyna e taw elen enian iyn Buk Baibel iyn e akwua ke akniaw re aij na kerꞌep aij remien reꞌe pene ves e na keniaw soene. 
\is2 Re kros-referens 
\ip 
\v 5 Taw on tartarna e akniaw re kros-referens kermen pepa taon. Re o soenere tortuiynjuiyna et re taw elen enian iyn Baibel kerꞌep re ves kerꞌep aij toko pene aij okon ves et tetꞌes nanekene peyian. E koluon akniaw elen kermen pepa ene taon.\f - \fr 2.10 \ft Hos 2.23\f*\f - \fr 2.22 \ft Ais 53.9\f*\f - \fr 2.23 \ft Ais 53.7\f*\f - \fr 2.24 \ft Ais 53.5,6\f* 
\is2 Re aij elen pene aij soene, koron re buk elen 
\ip 
\v 6 Tem elen, re niy iyn na karꞌar re buk iyn Buk Baibel ene, karꞌar re aij elen pene soene, koron re taw elen reꞌe buk elen iyn Buk Baibel ene. O ene tokꞌusia tem tartar koron re gutnius. Taako ekmen Luk 2.1 sopene. 
\s1 Maria koꞌow Jisas 
\r (Matyu 1.18-25) 
\ip 
\v 7 Aij akon yenama na aij noꞌuan ene, iyn toktuiynjuiyna pene, Matyu 1.18-25, yipe tawana tekesna aij iyn Maria koꞌow Jisas. 
\is2 Gloseri — Aij remien reꞌe aij elen 
\ip 
\v 8 Tem elen akꞌies aij koron buk iyn Luk ene ke akniaw re aij elen e lin awkuo sawe na aij remien reꞌe. Kopene \xt 1Pi 2.6\xt* keꞌep aij iyn Jisas \w Krais\w* ono \w at omon peyian\w* iyn toko olon. Akniaw re mak welen koron tenien iyn aij soenere. Re mak ene tortuiynjuiyna e pene aij ene okon Gloseri. Ke pene e akniaw Gloseri, e akniaw aij ene ekmen ke e akniaw piksa taako tawana. 
\b 
\ip \k At omon peyian\k* 
\v 9 \zge cornerstone\zge* \wg ἀκρογωνιαῖος, κεφαλὴν γωνίας\wg* Ene at prum taako re toroꞌiw yi tokon merꞌer peyian tokon tenien iyn olon ono ke re at elen torꞌotpem yi ke elen tortona yi torto merꞌer peyian ke olon awto nokuon. At ene toko moiyl pene peken toko iyn olon ete PNG. \xt Mt 21.42, Mk 12.10, Lk 20.17, Ap 4.11, 1Pi 2.7.\xt* 
\is2 Re leta teweiyn 
\ip 
\v 10 Taw elen, e akniaw leta teweiyn \sc pene re leta teweiyn ene.\sc* Et taꞌar leta sopenere iyn taꞌar aan iyn Godꞌe taw tartar iyn Olpela Testamen sopene: \nd Niy Prum\nd*. Na tem Aposel Pol kaꞌar aij na alapan yiꞌe antan, et taꞌar leta sopenere tawana. Ekniaw \xt Ga 6.11, Kl 4.18, 2Te 3.17, Fl 1.19\xt*. 
\is2 Speling reꞌe nem koron Baibel 
\ip 
\v 11 Re trensleta iyn buk ene karwanan tawantan iyn speling re niy iyn Baibel Sosaiti karwanan tem re karꞌapala Buk Baibel ke karꞌar niy aare. 
